tag_list: dominika-wolski, actress, writer, founder, environmentalist, romantic, explorer
overview:
Modern media musketeer, girl Indiana Jones. “fearless”

Actress/writer: CBC award winning series. Founder, Flikdate. Spokesmodel AZADA and Drive Around the World. Face of Froote jewelry.

A true idealist, and revisionist; some people set out to exist in history, others hope and aspire to influence and inspire it with life and vision. To give back. One part explorer, 13% dreamer, unquestionably passionate and yes, sometimes feisty.
